last_episode_to_air.name: Chijoku Shinsatsushitsu (Doctor Shameless)
last_episode_to_air.overview: Shinji Ishida is a doctor who works in a hospital on the verge of collapse. People have heard that this doctor has brought many hospitals back from financial ruin, but the method you might see is "unusual." After the session the patient cannot get enough natural treatment from him.
